                    img(src="http://localhost:3000/assets/images/add-blue-icon.svg", 
                        width="21", 
                        height="21") 
                    a.btn-link(href="/proposal/new") Cadastrar Nova Proposta
                li 
                    img(src="http://localhost:3000/assets/images/user-blue-icon.svg", 
                        width="24", 
                        height="32") 
                    a.btn-link(href="/users") Consultar Usuários
                li 
                    img(src="http://localhost:3000/assets/images/adduser-blue-icon.svg", 
